GREENWAY BREWING CO., Appellant, v. BISHOP, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. December 8, 1893.) Action by the Greenway Brewing Company against James L. Bishop.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment of the county court modified by striking therefrom the provision which awards a new trial, and as so modified affirmed, without costs to either party on this appeal.
